import { Box, Grid } from '@mui/material'
import { Container } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
    <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            Contact Us
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={7}>
            Form
        </Grid>
    </Grid>


    </Container>
  )
}

export default Contact
